About us
Since 1985 Sundowners restaurant in Key Largo has been serving sunsets, sandwiches, steaks and seafood on the Florida Bay. We serve the freshest seafood in town! Enjoy the view from our glass-walled dining room, sit outside on our covered deck, or tropical patio right on the Florida Bay. While dining at Sundowners, make sure to visit our back dock to take pictures of our one of a kind sunsets!
For groups and weddings, Sundowners can accommodate up to 100 guests for inside seating, and up to 200 guests for outside seating.
